{
  "texts": [
    "In the future, how to further strengthen the robustness of the method in practical situation s is one of the future research focuses.",
    "(2) Real-time processing of massive point cloud data in large-scale situations.",
    "In order to apply point cloud registration to actual medical image guidance, intelligent vehicles, and other fields, efficient real-time performance is needed.",
    "Due to the complex network structure, it is often difficult for the proposed methods to process massive point cloud data quickly.",
    "Therefore, while ensuring the effectiveness of the method, improving the real-time performance of the method is also the focus of future re-search."
  ]
}